{"tid":685727,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有無咩起野game好玩?","createTime":"2018-05-31T15:46:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T19:00:32.000Z","uid":27609,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e9d1a859daf4fc9d85d1877b8deed0a3667aa322","tid":685727,"uid":27609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T15:46:25.000Z","msg":"拋磚 Frostpunk <br />\n<br />\n社群生存遊戲<br />\n<br />\n《Frostpunk》是一款「社群生存」(society survival) 遊戲，這一次求生的不是一兩個平民，而是整個社群。玩家帶領著一小隊生還者，圍繞著一部蒸汽發電機生活，開採煤礦、一步步建立自己的城市，並試圖探索外面的世界。城市一旦沒有足夠的燃料、食物或房屋，你的人民便會生病甚至死亡。在資源有限的情況下，你必須決定滿足哪些需求，犧牲哪些人，為整個社群作長遠的打算。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.frostpunkgame.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/frostpunk_screenshot_06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.frostpunkgame.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F08%2Ffrostpunk_screenshot_06.jpg&h=5cbd5032&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b80e3d144e470b96050d56cc1b873192ecadbde","tid":685727,"uid":20119,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T02:56:21.000Z","msg":"Fortnite"},{"pid":"8175594018036d4a2503b8d10e7125a0bd68eca9","tid":685727,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:10:59.000Z","msg":"等緊jurassic world"},{"pid":"1d4bb7c555acd01b557fcba8ef002a032566dd3c","tid":685727,"uid":85722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:12:19.000Z","msg":"Sim city 2000"},{"pid":"81a42ec8e1993a58c59ae335ce0a1a1a16e7813f","tid":685727,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:17:56.000Z","msg":"fortnite"},{"pid":"d59b322c5531a459aa65e49e18e1dbd55ccc0c0a","tid":685727,"uid":144064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:49:22.000Z","msg":"civilization"},{"pid":"063687d5284df69848be51af5f032e75ffd3e5a2","tid":685727,"uid":182124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:53:27.000Z","msg":"aoc"},{"pid":"bbaffe15ee8bb04149397ba